This is a funny map with alot of secrets.
i have spent over 50 hours making this map.

There are no buyzones on this map, but there is weapons hidden around the map. (inside spawn, spawn roof, underground armory, snipers at container or car, inside security control room)


Look at screenshots for keypad codes. 

oh btw, there is a spot in a corner in spawns that leads to the underground. (shoot at the floor) same goes for the security room.
